OL,3,CWhich European countries are moving
OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FSpain has closed off its airspace to
OL,10,Fall US planes involved in the war in
OL,11,FIran, having already said the US was
OL,12,Fnot allowed to use jointly operated
OL,13,Fmilitary bases in the country for
OL,14,Foperations involved in the conflict.
OL,16,FThe Spanish government has been one of
OL,17,Fthe most vocal in Europe when it comes
OL,18,Fto criticising US President Donald
OL,19,FTrump and his actions in the Middle
OL,20,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
