OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775207142
OL,3,CWhich European countries are moving
OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,FBut it is not the only Western country
OL,7,Fmoving away from supporting the
OL,8,Fworld's most powerful nation in the
OL,9,Fconflict. ITV News explains.
OL,11,FSpanish Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez
OL,12,Fhas repeatedly called on the US,
OL,13,FIsrael and Iran to end the war, which
OL,14,Fhe described as "illegal", "reckless"
OL,15,Fand "unjust".
OL,17,F"You cannot respond to one illegality
OL,18,Fwith another, because that's how
OL,19,Fhumanity's great disasters begin," he
OL,20,Fsaid earlier this month.
