OL,3,CWhich European countries are moving
OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,FDefence Minister Margarita Robles said
OL,7,Fthat the same logic applied to the
OL,8,FUnited States' use of Spanish airspace.
OL,10,F"This was made perfectly clear to the
OL,11,FAmerican military and forces from the
OL,12,Fvery beginning. Therefore, neither the
OL,13,Fbases are authorised, nor, of course,
OL,14,Fis the use of Spanish airspace
OL,15,Fauthorised for any actions related to
OL,16,Fthe war in Iran," Robles told
OL,17,Freporters, describing the conflict as
OL,18,F"profoundly illegal and profoundly
OL,19,Funjust".
