OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,F"But if NATO is just about us
OL,7,Fdefending Europe if they're attacked,
OL,8,Fbut then denying us basing rights when
OL,9,Fwe need them, that's not a very good
OL,10,Farrangement," Rubio told Al Jazeera on
OL,11,FMonday.
OL,13,F"That's a hard one to stay engaged in
OL,14,Fand say this is good for the United
OL,15,FStates. So all of that is going to
OL,16,Fhave to be reexamined."
