OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,FTrump had already threatened to cut
OL,7,Ftrade with Madrid after Sanchez's
OL,8,Fgovernment denied the US use of the
OL,9,FRota and Moron military bases in
OL,10,Fsouthern Spain.
OL,12,FAt the start of the current conflict
OL,13,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron said
OL,14,Fthe US and Israeli strikes on Iran
OL,15,Fthat killed the country's supreme
OL,16,Fleader were "outside of international
OL,17,Flaw" and that Paris "cannot approve of
OL,18,Fthem".
