OL,3,CWhich European countries are moving
OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,FMacron said that France's
OL,7,F"credibility" was at stake and its
OL,8,Fpriority was to honour defence
OL,9,Fagreements with allies such as Kuwait,
OL,10,FQatar and the United Arab Emirates,
OL,11,Fwhere around 800 military personnel
OL,12,Fare stationed.
OL,14,FIn the following weeks the French
OL,15,Fpresident made it clear that he had no
OL,16,Fintentions for France to follow the US
OL,17,Finto the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
