OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,F"We are not party to the conflict and
OL,7,Ftherefore France will never take part
OL,8,Fin operations to open or liberate the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz in the current
OL,10,Fcontext," Macron said at the start of
OL,11,Fa cabinet meeting on March 17.
OL,13,FWhile Macron has not been directly
OL,14,Fcritical of the US president, some of
OL,15,Fhis comments could allude to the
OL,16,FStates being unpredictable in its
OL,17,Factions in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
