OL,4,Caway from Trump?
OL,6,F"I'm well aware that sometimes Europe
OL,7,Fcan be seen as a continent that is
OL,8,Fslower than others," Macron told
OL,9,FJapanese business leaders and
OL,10,Finvestors in Tokyo on Wednesday.
OL,12,F"But predictability has value, and we
OL,13,Fhave demonstrated that over all these
OL,14,Fpast years and, dare I say, even these
OL,15,Fpast weeks: we are where you know we
OL,16,Fwill go."
OL,18,FThe US has been more forthcoming in
OL,19,Fits criticism of France.
