OL,6,FOn Tuesday Trump claimed the country
OL,7,Fwas "very unhelpful" as it "wouldn't
OL,8,Flet planes headed to Israel, loaded up
OL,9,Fwith military supplies, fly over
OL,10,FFrench territory", saying the US
OL,11,F"would remember".
OL,13,FGerman Chancellor Friedrich Merz was
OL,14,Fslower to criticise Trump than his
OL,15,FFrench and Spanish counterparts, but
OL,16,Fon March 13 Merz said the war raised
OL,17,F"major questions" about security.
