OL,6,F"It is having a massive impact on our
OL,7,Fenergy costs, and it has the potential
OL,8,Fto trigger large-scale migration," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FDefence minister Boris Pistorius was
OL,12,Fmore disparaging in his remarks.
OL,14,F"What does ... Donald Trump expect a
OL,15,Fhandful or two handfuls of European
OL,16,Ffrigates to do in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,17,Fthat the powerful US Navy cannot do?"
OL,18,Fhe said last month.
OL,20,F"This is not our war; we have not
OL,21,Fstarted it."
