OL,6,FEven the country's far-right party,
OL,7,FAlternative for Germany, which has
OL,8,Flong presented itself as Germany's
OL,9,Fnatural ally to Trump, has commented
OL,10,Fon the US president's actions.
OL,12,F"Donald Trump started out as a peace
OL,13,Fpresident - he will end up as a war
OL,14,Fpresident," AfD co-leader Tino
OL,15,FChrupalla said on March 18.
