OL,6,F"The government's policy line is
OL,7,Fclear, consistent and has already been
OL,8,Ffully shared with Parliament, and
OL,9,Fremains unchanged."
OL,11,FPrime Minister Giorgia Meloni was the
OL,12,Fonly European head of government
OL,13,Finvited to Trump's inauguration, and
OL,14,Fhas been considered one of his closest
OL,15,Fallies in the bloc, but even she has
OL,16,Fdescribed the US actions in Iran
OL,17,F"outside the scope of international
OL,18,Flaw".
