OL,6,FThe UK reportedly refused American
OL,7,Frequests to use UK bases for
OL,8,Foperations against Iran, but that
OL,9,Fstance changed on March 1.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,12,Fhe had granted the request "to prevent
OL,13,FIran firing missiles across the
OL,14,Fregion, killing innocent civilians,
OL,15,Fputting British lives at risk, and
OL,16,Fhitting countries that have not been
OL,17,Finvolved".
OL,19,FTrump meanwhile has repeatedly hit out
OL,20,Fat the British leader.
OL,26,@tD@\OUyD@IO]
