OL,6,FWhen asked by reporters if his
OL,7,Frelationship with Starmer has been
OL,8,Fdamaged by the UK's stance over the
OL,9,Fwar, Trump said: "Well, he hasn't been
OL,10,Fsupportive, and I think it's a big
OL,11,Fmistake."
OL,13,FThe president added that he was
OL,14,F"disappointed" with Starmer, accusing
OL,15,Fthe prime minister of being "willing
OL,16,Fto send two aircraft carriers after we
OL,17,Fwon" on March 17.
