OL,7,Fprovide vessels to help open the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz and complained that
OL,9,FStarmer had so far declined to commit
OL,10,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,12,FHe also criticised British military
OL,13,Fprovisions, saying the British
OL,14,Faircraft carriers HMS Queen Elizabeth
OL,15,Fand HMS Prince of Wales were "toys"
OL,16,Fcompared to what the US has.
OL,18,FOpposition leader Kemi Badenoch also
OL,19,Fcriticised the US president.
